<h1>ReliefSim</h1>
<p>Funded by the Andrew W. Mellon Foundation, the ReliefSim project developed a prototype simulation that could be
used for training in complex humanitarian emergencies. Working with the Refugee Studies Centre at the University of Oxford,
Columbia University and various humanitarian NGOs, TALL contributed to the shaping of the project and provided pedagogical
consultancy to ensure effective learning.</p>


